OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear and
OL,6,Fdry for many overnight, perhaps with
OL,7,Fpatchy low cloud bringing misty
OL,8,Fconditions over some hills later in
OL,9,Fthe night. A rather chilly night with
OL,10,Fpockets of grass frost possible in
OL,11,Fsheltered rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FEarly cloud soon lifting to
OL,14,Fleave a fine day. After a cool start,
OL,15,Fsoon feeling warm with plenty of
OL,16,Fstrong April sunshine despite a breeze
OL,17,Fnear coasts and hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
