OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fthroughout the week with high pressure
OL,7,Fdominating. Often sunny and feeling
OL,8,Fwarm by day. Chilly nights with rural
OL,9,Ffrosts possible as winds ease.
OL,10,FCloudier into the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
